						<p>Cites details of a date namely, <hi rend="bold">Dhanus, śu. 15, Wednesday and Tiruvādirai</hi> and refers to an endowment for various services in the temple and mentions Anantāḻvār Bhaṭṭar, son of Śrīraṅgarāja Bhaṭṭar of Uttiramērūr. See No. 397 above, which contains a reference to the donor's other gifts.</p>						

